# Bitstream-Studio rules

## Repository layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| **`extension/`** | VS Code extension + webview + `src/bitstream2/` |
| **`AGENT_HANDOFF.md`** | Session onboarding |
| **`.cursor/rules/`** | Agent policy |
| **`.cursor/skills/`** | Project skills (dev, protocol, UART, simulator) |

**Not in this repo:** `T3D/`, `bitstream-simulator/` (separate VSIX).

## Development

- Work in **`extension/`**: `npm install`, `npm run start:bridge`, `npm run dev:webview`, `npm run compile`.
- Dev URLs: `http://localhost:5173/?app=bitstream`, `?app=sensor-studio`.
- Runbook: **`extension/HOW_TO_RUN.md`**. Skill: **`bitstream-studio-dev`**.

## BS2 protocol (canonical in this repo)

| Doc | Path |
|-----|------|
| Index | **`extension/docs/BS2_PROTOCOL_INDEX.md`** |
| Wire spec | **`extension/docs/BITSTREAM_BS_FRAMED_PROTOCOL_SPEC.md`** |
| Host code | **`extension/src/bitstream2/`** |

Protocol changes: **`.cursor/rules/bs2-protocol-change.mdc`**, skill **`bs2-protocol-change`**.

## No `@ternion/t3d`

Decoupling complete (2026-05-30). Local **`ui/catalog/`**, **`extension-bridge/`**, vendored CSS — no npm `@ternion/t3d`.

## VSIX

- Extension id: **`bitstream-studio`** (v0.1.0).
- **`isVsCodeExtensionWebview()`** / `window.__VSCODE_API__` — not `T3DVSCodeUtils.isVsCodeMode()` alone.
- Re-test after **`npm run package`** in a clean VS Code window.

## Related rules

- **`bitstream-studio-handoff.mdc`**, **`bs2-protocol-change.mdc`**, **`bitstream-dual-runtime.mdc`**, **`bitstream-simulator-app-path.mdc`**, **`tesaiot-firmware-bitstream-paths.mdc`**

## Communication

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese.** Use **English** and/or **Thai** only — **`communication-language.mdc`**.
